title: Car dealership network sizes in the United Kingdom ( UK ) 2014 to 2017
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 28 different Car Manufacturers on X-axis for 2 groups July 2014, and January 2017. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
Car Manufacturer Ford had the maximum SOME LABEL among all 2 groups, and it was for July 2014. The minimum SOME LABEL was observed in Car Manufacturer Mercedes for July 2014.
Among all the Car Manufacturers, January 2017 had the highest SOME LABEL 475.0 in Car Manufacturer Ford and lowest value 38.0 in Car Manufacturer Mercedes.
The maximum SOME LABEL for January 2017 that was found in Car Manufacturer Ford was 12.5 times larger than the minimum SOME LABEL observed in Car Manufacturer Mercedes.
